[30;1m1665 | [0m[35m    The `impute` parameter tells Hail to scan the file an extra time to gather[0m
[30;1m1666 | [0m[35m    information about possible field types. While this is a bit slower for large[0m
[30;1m1667 | [0m[35m    files because the file is parsed twice, the convenience is often worth this[0m
[30;1m1668 | [0m[35m    cost.[0m
